name.sl: Odločite se med klasično nogometno tekmo in obračunom na univerzi. Retro Bowl College je originalna zgodba ogridnih količin nogometne zabave in dveh epskih tekmovanjih za naslov najboljšega nogometaša! Pripravite se na kopico srednjeveških akcij s sovražnimi študenti, nesporazumi s profesorji, zgodbe iz stražarjev in edinstvenimi odpadki, ki sovražijo vaš posel.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
🏈 Experience college football like never before with Retro Bowl! 🏈

Relive the glory days of NCAA football in this retro-style game. Build your dream college program into a national powerhouse. 💪

⏩ Fast-paced, arcade-style gameplay
⭐ Recruit fresh talent and develop players
🏆 Win conference titles and national championships
🌟 Unlock legendary coaches from college football history

🚀 Choose from over 100 unique teams
🏟️ Customize home stadium atmosphere
🔥 Unleash special team playbooks

Will you establish a new dynasty? 🤔 Or lead a Cinderella underdog story? 😲 The choice is yours!

Lead your team to victory in single player season mode or intense multiplayer leagues. The spirit of college football awaits! 🏈

Get ready to experience the passion and tradition of NCAA football like never before. Download now!
